title: For Sale/Trade:  Bullpup Mini 14 Stainless Steel
postcontent:
This gun is my baby I have put a lot of hard work and love into it. Parting with it isn't easy however I want a new project. It is a late 90's model stainless steel mini 14 in perfect shape and clean as a whistle. Mini 14's are one of the most reliable 223. on the market and my bullet count speaks for itself.		
   I have put aprox. 350-400rds down range (broken in) smooth as silk never a stovepipe nor a jam with the Ruger clips at least. The off brand ones I can’t say the same. You can only load 29 out of 30rds or you will get a stovepipe on the last round. With the bullpup stock I have had 2in groupings at 50yrds and 3½in at 75yrds.  This is perfect for home defense with it only being 26½ inches long it is very light and maneuverable. The red dot clone sight has a green setting for night vision they are both very bright and both have 10x brightness settings.  The only real difference between this and an Eotech is the dots for droppage are nonexistent but you can guestimate for range. Anyone who says otherwise is just sore because they over paid. The UTG flashlight is bright as hell! It would blind a burglar in a flash. Everything I have changed on this gun was done with no gunsmithing and is completely reversible should you want to switch back to the original hardware. I will include all original furniture with purchase which includes a rugged rubber black Houge stock and the original rear sight. The bayonet lug/front sight I sold to a friend but they run around 25 bucks. 				
   This is a great starter gun for people who want to tinker or modify as it is so easy to disassemble and clean and there are lots of accessories. It is also a good rifle for people who are new to firearms as the kick is low and the sound is mild. I have modified this gun into a bullpup and added a few home defense base accessories great for any survival situation or just plinking at the range. It is painted using local flora and Krylon camouflage paint. 

What you will get….										                
-Stainless steel Ruger Mini-14 MSRP-$550.00

-Muzzelite Bullpup Stock with rails- (http://www.mountsplus.com/AR-15_Accessories/AR-15_Scope_Rings/MZ-14-PLUS.html) MSRP- $139.00

-UTG 126 Lumen tactical flashlight MSRP- $33.00

-Eotech clone sight- MSRP-88.00 

-dust cover- MSRP-$40.00

-limbsaver butt pad-MSRP-$25.00

- six clips total- MSRP-$60.00
•	one 20shot Ruger clip(blued) original came with gun.
•	one 20shot Mil Spec stainless steel clip.
•	four 30shot Mil Spec stainless steel clips.

Total-550+139+33+88+40+25+60= $935.00 but my price $850.00 firm
